#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introduction"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kooka; is a &kde; application that enables easy scanning using "
#| "<acronym>SANE</acronym> libraries. Therefore,<acronym>SANE</acronym> the "
#| "package must be installed to use &kooka;. Clear and concise use was the "
#| "focus of its development."
msgid ""
"&kooka; is an application that provides access to scanner hardware using the "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/\">SANE</ulink> library. Therefore, "
"the <acronym>SANE</acronym> package must be installed to use &kooka;."
msgstr ""
"&kooka; est une application &kde; qui vous permet un accès facile à un "
"scanner grâce aux bibliothèques <acronym>SANE</acronym>. De ce fait, le "
"paquetage <acronym>SANE</acronym> doit être installé avant d'utiliser "
"&kooka;. Une utilisation simple est le but de son développement."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kooka; allows you to scan, save and view in any image format that &Qt; "
"supports."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Character recognition is also provided by using the open source <ulink url="
"\"http://jocr.sourceforge.net/\">GOCR</ulink> or <ulink url=\"http://www.gnu."
"org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html\">OCRAD</ulink> programs, or the commercial "
"<ulink url=\"https://rerecognition.com/en/products/kadmos-icr-ocr/\">KADMOS</"
"ulink> library. You have to install at least one of these software packages "
"to use this functionality. After character recognition is complete, a "
"spellcheck is automatically started for the recognized material. You can "
"edit the content in the <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> window and export it as "
"plain text."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Instructions"
msgstr "Instructions pour l'application"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The web site <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/\">http://www.sane-"
"project.org</ulink> has information about supported scanners. Refer to it "
"before purchasing a scanner, if possible."
msgstr ""
"Le site web <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/\">http://www.sane-"
"project.org</ulink> donne des informations sur les scanners pris en charge. "
"Rapportez-vous-y avant d'acheter un scanner si possible."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The &kooka; Main Window</title>"
msgstr "<title>La fenêtre principale de &kooka;</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &kooka; Main Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>La fenêtre principale de &kooka;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Start &kooka; from a console by simply entering "
#| "<userinput><command>kooka</command></userinput>. Create a link on the "
#| "&kde; desktop, which uses a scanner icon, if desired."
msgid ""
"Start &kooka; from a console by simply entering <userinput><command>kooka</"
"command></userinput> or select it from the <guilabel>Graphics</guilabel> "
"submenu in the application starter. Create a link on the desktop, which uses "
"a scanner icon, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Démarrez &kooka; à partir d'une console en écrivant simplement "
"<userinput><command>kooka</command></userinput>. Créez un lien sur le bureau "
"de &kde; qui utilise une icône de scanner si vous le désirez."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use &kooka; only for optical character recognition without connecting to "
"a scanner start the application in gallery mode with "
"<userinput><command>kooka</command> <option>-g</option></userinput>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main window in &kooka; consists of three frames. At the top, see both "
"icon and a menu panels. Use the mouse to enlarge or reduce the windows as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"La fenêtre principale de &kooka; consiste en trois cadres. En haut, vous "
"voyez deux panneaux, l'un d'icônes et l'un de menus. Utilisez la souris pour "
"agrandir ou réduire les fenêtres selon les besoins."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The navigation window consists of two tabs, which allow you to switch "
#| "between the <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> and the integrated file browser "
#| "called the <guilabel>Gallery</guilabel>. The working folder is displayed "
#| "in the lower part of the window along with the folder where the scan will "
#| "be saved."
msgid ""
"The navigation window consists of three tabs, which allow you to switch "
"between the <guilabel>Scan</guilabel>, <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> and the "
"integrated file browser called the <guilabel>Gallery</guilabel>. The working "
"folder is displayed in the upper part of the window along with the folder "
"where the scan will be saved."
msgstr ""
"La fenêtre de navigation consiste en deux onglets, qui vous permettent de "
"basculer entre <guilabel>Aperçu</guilabel> et le navigateur intégré nommé "
"<guilabel>Images</guilabel> Le dossier de travail est affiché dans la partie "
"basse de la fenêtre le long du dossier où l'image scannée peut être "
"enregistrée."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make your scanner-dependent settings, which are dependent on the scanner you "
"have connected, in the lower left window. Usually, these are settings for "
"resolution, brightness and contrast, scanning mode (&eg;, color, gray, or "
"binary), and for gamma values."
msgstr ""
"Faites vos réglages qui concernent le scanner et qui sont dépendants du "
"modèle que vous avez connecté dans la fenêtre en bas à gauche. "
"Habituellement, ce sont des réglages pour la résolution, la luminosité et le "
"contraste, le mode d'acquisition (&pex; couleur, gris ou binaire) et pour "
"les valeurs gamma."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Configure your settings here first. Afterwards, initiate the preview scan "
#| "with <guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem>. If the <guilabel>Preview</"
#| "guilabel> tab in the upper window is selected, see the results there."
msgid ""
"Configure your settings here first. Afterwards, initiate the preview scan "
"with <guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem>. The scan result will then appear in "
"the right pane."
msgstr ""
"Configurez vos réglages d'abord ici. Après, initiez la prévisualisation avec "
"<guimenuitem>Aperçu</guimenuitem>. Si l'onglet <guilabel>Aperçu</guilabel> "
"dans la fenêtre du haut est sélectionné, voyez les résultats ici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the area to scan in the preview image itself with the mouse to define "
"the final dimensions."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After this is done, click <guimenu>Scan</guimenu> to scan the selection made "
"in the preview. After scanning, you will be asked in which format to save "
"the image whether to make this your standard format (without being prompted "
"to confirm your selection in the future)."
msgstr ""
"Après que c'est fait, cliquez sur <guimenu>Numérisation</guimenu> pour "
"scanner la sélection faite dans l'aperçu. Après l'acquisition, on vous "
"demandera dans quel format enregistrer l'image et si vous en faites votre "
"format par défaut (sans qu'on vous demande de confirmation à l'avenir)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you checked that you do not want to be asked about the save format, "
#| "the memory assistant will no longer appear. To change the format some "
#| "time in the future, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Configure Kooka...</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Save Image</"
#| "guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Always show memory assistant</guimenuitem> </"
#| "menuchoice>"
msgid ""
"If you checked that you do not want to be asked about the save format, the "
"memory assistant will no longer appear. To change the format some time in "
"the future, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Kooka...</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Image Saving</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Always use the Save Assistant</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Si vous avez coché que vous ne voulez pas qu'on vous demande le format "
"d'enregistrement, l'assistant de mémorisation n'apparaîtra plus. Pour "
"changer le format à l'avenir, sélectionnez "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configurer Kooka..."
"</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Enregistrement de l'image</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Toujours afficher l'assistant d'enregistrement "
"d'image</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "The large window shows how the image appears after a final scan."
msgstr ""
"La grande fenêtre montre comment les images apparaissent après une "
"acquisition finale."

